                            <comment id="100726" author="adilger" created="Thu, 4 Dec 2014 19:31:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like there may be a defect in the test.  In the DNE striped directory case, there is nothing to constrain the files being created to the same MDT as the number of precreated files that were checked at the start.  I think the test needs to be fixed to create a non-striped directory on a single MDT (probably $SINGLEMDS where the precreated objects are checked).&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
